siapa yang Anda tangkap?

00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:40.720
Dia adalah Shiv Kashyap!

00:22:43.680 --> 00:22:45.400
Putra Raghunath Kashyap!

00:22:48.000 --> 00:22:49.280
